<P>
   &UR; WASHINGTON (w) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   GORE-PRESIDENCY (Washington) _ Vice President Al Gore admits
he's been focused more on California than on New Hampshire. That
will change with his visit Monday, but he shouldn't expect a
cakewalk in New England. By Ann Scales. (w and a coding)
</P>
<P>
