<P>
   &UR; NATIONAL (a) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   ALAMOS-SPY (Los Alamos, N.M.) _ Los Alamos, cold-war redoubt
off-limits to civilians until 1957, is shaken by a spy scandal. By
Lynda Gorov. 1300 words. &UR;  &LR; GRAPHIC: 25 picas x 8.5 inches, ``Inside
