1988 ! 11 ! 9 ! 16 ! 13 &QL; 
1995 ! 19 ! 16 ! 31 ! 24 &QL; 
 &QL; 
SOURCES: National Center for Health Statistics, Urban Institute &QL;
</P>
</TEXT>
