   &UR; NATIONAL GENERAL &LR;  (``w'' code)
</P>
<P>
   CHURCH-SHOOTING (Gonzales, La.) _ The pastor had just started
reading a Bible lesson about being born again when the gunman
kicked open the doors and started shooting as screaming
parishioners scattered in horror. The gunman shot and killed his
wife, young son and another churchgoer and left at least two others
in critical condition. Police later found that he had killed his
mother-in-law before the church attack. By David Firestone.
</P>
<P>
   With map.
</P>
<P>
   YOSEMITE-MISSING (San Francisco) _ The FBI holds a briefing on
the case of a woman, daughter and friend who disappeared in
Yosemite. By Evelyn Nieves.
