<P>
   DATE-RAPE _ WASHINGTON _ A House Commerce subcommittee holds a
hearing on ``date rape'' drugs. (Dart, Cox News Service).
</P>
<P>
   BRYOZOAN _ WASHINGTON The federal judge who has temporarily
halted a Corps of Engineers beach nourishment project near Fort
Pierce, Fla., because the corps failed to consider the impact the
project might have on several species of obscure aquatic creatures
called bryozoans meets with lawyers and environmentalists
challenging the project Thursday to where the case goes next.
(Nesmith, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
