<P>
   UNDATED _ If you just got your pink slip or see it coming, don't
despair _ get a lawyer. Or at least get your hands on a copy of
``Getting Fired: What to do if you're fired, downsized, laid off,
restructured, discharged, terminated, or forced to resign'' (Warner
Books, 370 pages, $24). By TERESA MCUSIC. Story has moved in ``f''
financial category. &QL; 
