   CAR-SADLER _ To say the burden is heavy on driver Elliott Sadler
is an understatement. Sadler has been annointed as the savior for
the legendary Woods Bros. team, who has struggled for many years.
We look at the pressures Sadler faces while trying to return the
Woods team to the glory days. (Levine, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 22.
