in Arizona history has been concluded. Sports team mogul John McCaw
has sold his 10-acre spread on the north side of Camelback Mountain
for $8.3 million. By CHARLES KELLY and CATHERINE REAGOR. Story will
move in the ``A'' category. &QL; 
