<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-11 19:40 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7005 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ELIMINATE-TRADES-SHOR     03-11 0033
