unveils a $21 million effort to bring religious conservatives to
the polls in the 2000 elections. ``We are launching, effective
today, the most massive effort to mobilize the (coalition's)
grass-roots in our history,'' evangelist and Christian Coalition
founder Pat Robertson says. By DAN FREEDMAN. (Already filed.)
</P>
