   JUSTICE-STARR (Washington) _ Deputy Attorney General Eric Holder
bluntly dismisses allegations that the Justice Department has tried
to hamper Independent Counsel Kenneth Starr's investigation of
President Clinton. By STEVE LASH. (Already filed.)
