to men, Hedda is, in some ways, to women,'' said Bening, the latest
Hedda, who will star in the play which begins previews Sunday
evening at the Geffen Playhouse in Westwood. (Monica Almeida/New
York Times Photo)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT4) NEW YORK -- March 11, 1999 -- ADV. FOR SUN., MARCH 14 --
