<HEADER>
A7184 &Cx1f; tic-z
u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  C-AZR-BUDGET-AZR &LR;      03-11 0038
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE>
 
</HEADLINE>
 C-AZR-BUDGET-AZR   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
BC- ELIMINATE_ELIMINATE-AZR
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   Budgeted Phoenix  &UR; NAVAJO-MEDICINE and  &UR; BIGHORN-HUNTER will not
move in  &UR; FRIDAY'S Arizona Republic report.
